<p>For better readability, do not put more than one statement on a single line.</p>
<h2>Noncompliant Code Example</h2>
<pre>
Module Module1
    Sub Main()
        Dim a = 0 : Dim b = 0  ' Noncompliant
    End Sub
End Module
</pre>
<h2>Compliant Solution</h2>
<pre>
Module Module1
    Sub Main()
        Dim a = 0              ' Compliant
        Dim b = 0              ' Compliant
    End Sub
End Module
</pre>